49:27.314 --> 49:29.305
I'll go with you if you want.

49:30.118 --> 49:32.279
I'm not going to do anything.

49:35.590 --> 49:39.048
This guy was... was some ex-con.

49:39.094 --> 49:41.392
Are you going to let him walk the streets?

49:41.429 --> 49:45.661
- What do you want me to do?
- He ran over Michael and your daughters...

49:45.700 --> 49:50.797
Nothing I can do is going to bring them back.
Do you get that?

50:01.284 --> 50:03.514
Hey, how are you doing?

50:03.553 --> 50:06.147
- You found it OK?
- Yeah, I did.

50:07.156 --> 50:10.990
The donor's name was Michael Peck.
He was 37 years old.

50:11.027 --> 50:13.120
An architect and married.

50:13.162 --> 50:17.690
