signed by his wife, Cristina Williams Peck.

50:17.733 --> 50:21.033
I have a copy of the medical report
if you'd care to see it

50:21.071 --> 50:25.838
And I also have the widow's phone number
and address if you're interested.

50:25.876 --> 50:28.436
