51:28.173 --> 51:30.164
What is, then?

51:33.178 --> 51:35.477
Look for it with me.

51:36.950 --> 51:39.976
Let's look ahead together, not behind.

51:53.233 --> 51:58.194
Not drinking on your birthday?
Come over to my place, I'm having a party.

51:58.239 --> 52:02.175
I bet they're all as boring as you.
You'd be surprised.

52:02.209 --> 52:05.872
- I'll pass. I call you later about that job.
- All right.

52:06.914 --> 52:08.575
Thank you.

52:12.153 --> 52:14.713
Hey, Brown, you should.

52:14.755 --> 52:16.746
I will.

52:48.958 --> 52:54.294
