about artificial insemination,

53:25.863 --> 53:30.596
Kids' names, we got pictures
of our friends' babies all over the place.

53:30.634 --> 53:33.797
Why? So you can flush it down the fucking toilet?

53:37.008 --> 53:40.273
We've been a fraud for a long time, Mary.

53:40.311 --> 53:43.474
