and have this baby.

54:35.102 --> 54:39.198
- When we could have, you didn't want to.
- We were separated, goddamnit!

54:39.239 --> 54:41.639
- It's different now.
- Yes.

54:41.675 --> 54:44.166
- It's different.
-

54:44.211 --> 54:47.908
